Our Services

{/* Program 1: Before After School Care */}

After School Care

At DStar, we are committed to nurturing the next generation of leaders and innovators through our carefully designed after-school care program. Our mission is to create a supportive, stimulating environment that enhances your child’s growth beyond the classroom. We offer:

  • Social skill development: Group activities and collaborative projects that build friendships and confidence.
  • Personalized academic support: Experienced teachers help with school homework, offering tailored guidance.
  • Creative enrichment: Activities like arts and presentations to spark curiosity and a love of learning.
  • Physical activity: Outdoor play and sports to promote health, teamwork, and fun.
  • Library visits: Encouraging a passion for reading with access to a diverse range of books.

Our caring teachers provide individualized attention, ensuring children thrive academically, socially, and emotionally.

{/* Program 2: Tuition Service */}

Tuition Service

From Primary 1 onwards, our qualified tutors offer personalized tuition services. We focus on academic excellence, ensuring each child’s unique learning needs are met with tailored support, taught by highly qualified teachers.

{/* Program 3: Enrichment Program */}

Enrichment Program

Our enrichment program offers children exciting activities like robotics, creative writing, and arts. These programs foster creativity, innovation, and critical thinking, helping children grow intellectually and emotionally.

{/* Program 4: School Holiday Program */}

School Holiday Program

Keep your child engaged during the holidays with our full-day holiday programs. Packed with fun and educational activities, our programs help children learn and grow while enjoying their time off from school.

); } export default ProgramsPage;
